00:31:06,930 --> 00:31:08,161
<i>So...</i>

769
00:31:08,163 --> 00:31:11,295
<i>The good news is that Sean
is home from London,</i>

770
00:31:11,297 --> 00:31:13,531
<i>and he's working very
