seems to give a crap.

832
00:33:27,796 --> 00:33:28,797
Excuse my language.

833
00:33:30,264 --> 00:33:31,894
- Kiko.
- Hmm?

834
00:33:31,896 --> 00:33:33,595
Why did Emily
go to Miami?

835
00:33:33,597 --> 00:33:34,964
I didn't know she did.

836
00:33:36,895 --> 00:33:38,893
We in this office
have learned that

837
