00:34:38,530 --> 00:34:40,893
WOMAN: No, I can't
help you with that.

855
00:34:40,895 --> 00:34:42,327
Of course he's
freaking out.

856
00:34:42,329 --> 00:34:44,728
He needs someone
to manage this now.

857
00:34:44,730 --> 00:34:45,897
