864
00:35:35,330 --> 00:35:36,764
Or just a common
garden shoplifter?

865
00:35:37,997 --> 00:35:39,861
Yeah, you gotta go
right at them.

866
00:35:39,863 --> 00:35:41,295
Especially
the powerful ones.

867
00:35:41,297 --> 00:35:42,896
Or they will fuck you
in the face.

868
00:35:43,997 --> 00:35:45,528
Listen, you bargain
basement Tom Ford,

869
00:35:45,530 --> 00:35:46,760
if you don't have
this Ken doll

