00:36:01,563 --> 00:36:02,894
they are not
Indonesian children,

878
00:36:02,896 --> 00:36:04,593
they are Vietnamese
teenagers.

879
00:36:04,595 --> 00:36:07,694
Number two,
Tom Ford wishes he were me.

880
00:36:07,696 --> 00:36:10,763
And number three,
if I'm tacky,

881
00:36:11,695 --> 00:36:12,763
okay?

