00:36:39,662 --> 00:36:41,761
Comforting
the worried husband.

889
00:36:41,763 --> 00:36:42,827
Oh, please.

890
00:36:42,829 --> 00:36:45,361
It's an arts
and crafts project.

891
00:36:45,363 --> 00:36:48,027
I've never seen her pass up
